headline: NASCAR Legend Richard Childress Is Sending A Million Rounds Of Ammo To Ukraine
author: David Hookstead
sentences: (Tweet/Video) According to Jenna Fryer, the former racer and current team owner told reporters in a recent call that he’s sending a million rounds of ammo through Ammo Inc. to Ukraine.
(Video) All eyes are on Ukraine as the nation attempts to repel a Russian invasion being carried out by Vladimir Putin’s forces.Well, help is on the way thanks to Childress.
(Tweet) Furthermore, he pointed out that the situation in Ukraine is a great reminder of why the Second Amendment is so important in America.
NASCAR legend Richard Childress is hellbent on helping the people of Ukraine.
